# If you prefer the allow list template instead of the deny list, see community template:
# https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/community/Golang/Go.AllowList.gitignore
#
# Binaries for programs and plugins
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binary, built with `go test -c`
*.test
debug.test*

# Code coverage profiles and other test artifacts
*.out
coverage.*
*.coverprofile
profile.cov

# Dependency directories (remove the comment below to include it)
# vendor/

# Go workspace file
go.work
go.work.sum

# env file
.env

# 项目级配置 dotdir（镜像 ~/.novel-studio/）：config.json 含密钥，rules/ 为本地写作偏好
.novel-studio/

# Editor/IDE
.idea/
.vscode/

# GoReleaser artifacts
dist/
release-notes.md
/novel-studio

tasks
refer/
output*
workspace/

# 长篇拆文工作区：保留说明和模板，忽略真实原文与拆解产物

# 拆解库内容不入库(仅保留结构说明与模板,见 deconstruction-library/README.md 的提交规则)
deconstruction-library/*
!deconstruction-library/README.md
deconstruction-library.zip

# 数据集(参考库/生成产物/运行工作区)不入库
data/

# 本地 embedding 模型权重(>100MB,下载方式见 models/embedding/README.md)
models/embedding/*.gguf

# Claude Code 本地会话配置
.claude/settings.local.json

# Python 缓存
__pycache__/
*.pyc
